on our daughter.

28:09.289 --> 28:12.025
‐ A student brought this
to my attention.

28:12.025 --> 28:14.561
[dance music playing,
laughter]

28:14.595 --> 28:17.564
[tense music]

28:17.598 --> 28:22.002
♪ ♪

28:22.002 --> 28:27.040
‐ [grunting]

28:27.040 --> 28:29.776
‐ What is this?
Her Halloween costume?

28:29.776 --> 28:36.116
‐ She's dressed up
like Lucas... My brother.

28:36.116 --> 28:39.686
Why would you let her do that?

28:39.686 --> 28:41.722
‐ Okay, look,
we all know that communicating

28:41.722 --> 28:44.658
