28:44.658 --> 28:46.693
I think we can all agree
the best thing is to go home,

28:46.693 --> 28:50.531
talk to your kids,
find a way to move forward.

29:01.808 --> 29:04.745
[dramatic music]

29:04.778 --> 29:06.747
♪ ♪

29:06.780 --> 29:10.083
[crow cawing]

29:27.734 --> 29:31.038
[wind whooshing]

29:34.208 --> 29:37.177
[bird calling]

29:37.211 --> 29:44.318
♪ ♪

29:50.057 --> 29:54.194
‐ Mom, you always said
it would get better,

29:54.194 --> 30:01.502
but it never did.
Everything just got worse.

30:07.508 --> 30:11.545
I don't expect you
to forgive me. And I'm‐‐

30:11.545 --> 30:18.585
I'm sorry I'm not the person
that you wanted me to be.

30:18.585 --> 30:21.555
[crickets chirping]

30:21.555 --> 30:25.225
‐ [sighs]

30:25.225 --> 30:27.161
Hey, it's time for bed.
Did you brush your teeth?

30:27.161 --> 30:30.531
‐ And Chucky's too.
‐ Good job.

30:30.531 --> 30:35.802
‐ Okay, go to sleep.
‐ You didn't do it right. ‐ What?

30:35.802 --> 30:38.138
‐ Bedtime.
You have to sing to me.

30:38.138 --> 30:44.244
Daddy sings to me.
‐ [laughing softly]

30:44.244 --> 30:48.182
‐ If you tell anyone
about this, I'll kill you.

30:48.182 --> 30:54.588
‐ I won't say a word. ‐ [sighs]

31:03.797 --> 31:06.266
[sighs]
Um...

31:07.801 --> 31:11.305
♪ La, la, la, la, la ♪

31:13.607 --> 31:16.443
