31:38.532 --> 31:43.170
♪ Baby, take my hand,
don't fear the reaper ♪

31:43.203 --> 31:48.175
♪ We'll be able to fly,
don't fear the reaper ♪

31:48.208 --> 31:51.144
[soft dramatic music]

31:51.178 --> 31:56.650
♪ ♪

31:56.650 --> 32:02.656
Okay.

32:02.656 --> 32:06.026
Okay.
Snug as a bug.

32:06.026 --> 32:08.629
‐ What about Chucky?

32:08.629 --> 32:12.166
‐ Snug as a bug.
