36:20.314 --> 36:26.053
‐ [sighs]
What a pain in the ass.

36:26.053 --> 36:28.355
Stupid doll.

36:28.355 --> 36:33.360
♪ ♪

36:33.393 --> 36:34.761
[sighs]

36:34.761 --> 36:39.800
Where the hell
