‐ [panting]

37:40.427 --> 37:47.301
‐ [grunts]

37:47.301 --> 37:49.403
Charles, run.

37:49.403 --> 37:54.374
♪ ♪

37:54.374 --> 37:56.677
‐ Charles?

37:56.677 --> 38:00.314
[gasps]
Charles, come on.

38:06.420 --> 38:11.758
Okay, in here.
It's okay, it's okay. Shh, shh.

38:11.758 --> 38:15.462
