38:55.769 --> 39:03.043
♪ ♪

39:11.518 --> 39:14.254
‐ Caroline, I can't find...

39:14.254 --> 39:16.957
[dance music fades in]

39:16.957 --> 39:20.594
Never mind.

39:20.594 --> 39:27.668
♪ ♪

39:32.806 --> 39:35.108
